description: Completely hands-free. No phones needed. Enjoy total freedom when jogging, traveling, or commuting to work. Vinci allows you to voice control your music when manually choosing songs on your phone is inconvenient. Say anything (artist, song, album, genre, mood) you want, Vinci will match songs to whatever you say, or let Vinci pick a song for you.Integrated music services, online or offline. Stream Spotify, SoundCloud, and Amazon Music directly on your headphones. Vinci also supports Amazon Alexa and you can call out Alexa services anywhere you go! Directly connect to Wi-Fi or 3G network to stream music or listen to your imported songs in Vinci’s local 16G storage (store up to 4000 mp3). You can also listen music from other devices via Bluetooth connection.Vinci is a standalone device with a powerful dual-core ARM Cortex-A7 processor, 16 GB of storage, and its own operating system. Vinci's platform technology is built in the cloud and is powered by natural language processing and artificial intelligence, so it gets smarter and smarter, learning from your speech patterns and preferences. Vinci senses and learns from your body vitals, activities, listening habits and preferences to make intelligent, real-time recommendations.Vinci is super-easy to use. Vinci headphones automatically play when they’re on your ears and pause when you remove them. Simply tap and swipe to adjust tracks and volume. Use hold-to-talk or simply say “Hi Vinci” to wake up the voice services3D sound recording and playback. Dual-microphones in close proximity to your ears provide binaural recording and re-create a 3D sound sensation. Up to 3 weeks standby time, 26 hours of music playback via Bluetooth, or 7 hours non-stop standalone music playback. Support standalone music playback, bluetooth music + calls and audio jack input.
